William was married to Audrey.
A memorial mass will be held on April 18 2016 at 10 am at St. Barnabas Church 1400 N Main St O'Fallon MO 63366.
In lieu of flowers family and friends wishing to honor William�s memory may contribute to the Parkinson�s Disease Foundation http:www.pdf.org or by mail 1359 Broadway Suite 1509 New York NY 10018.




